利兮騅不逝。騅不逝兮可奈何，虞兮虞兮奈若何？」虞姬自刎殉情，項羽悲傷不已。後與八百騎突圍不果，鏖戰後於烏江自刎而死。<br />\n<br />\n此劇原名《楚漢爭》，根據崑曲《千金記》和《史記&middot;項羽本紀》編寫而成。總共四本。1918年，由楊小樓、尚小雲在北京首演。1922年2月15日，楊小樓與梅蘭芳合作。齊如山、吳震修對《楚漢爭》進行修改，更名為《霸王別姬》。<br />\n<br />\nWiki."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"你真係覺得講呢個咩"},{"pid":"6426784030119e769ecc4f86f8979604a005f061","tid":762120,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b5c7819196f4ac65edf0037755922a560f1f1ca","tid":762120,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"89eadc482b8ad5826a92076e58dd1d704b269264","tid":762120,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"94862c3aa8fa6507e09470b2649123b1a1bb9e3a","tid":762120,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"佢地撚識咩<br />\n連簡可以解做揀都唔識啦<br />\n出師表都有<br />\n是以先帝簡拔以遺陛下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"五毛十卜ching<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/123115_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F123115_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=44c498b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"關蛇駁唔到就玩貼圖？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"五毛係你身份<br />\n唔係駁你<br />\n婊子一定係蝗語唔使拗<br />\n你拎出師表出嚟做乜鳩？"},{"pid":"ac34214adc00d34b691ce83304ad7d088d7a3d34","tid":762120,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55beb37f40f25f9651adc1d4ccfa5a3697495762","tid":762120,"uid":34602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ad61f69a5683e9c7e2e91b8ddc63020f123a2660","tid":762120,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"霸王別姬故事發生地方係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"